{"tid":1173972,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】瘋傳疑似姚子羚床片 網民:把聲一定係佢","createTime":"2019-05-27T13:23:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:06:00.000Z","uid":66271,"like":32,"dislike":233,"uniUserReply":90,"replies":[{"pid":"a0dd7cd371493ecdf0462a0ca0347e2dddc6a7fb","tid":1173972,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:23:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://iso2.cx/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/%E7%98%8B%E5%82%B3%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%A7%9A%E5%AD%90%E7%BE%9A%E5%BA%8A%E7%89%87.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiso2.cx%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F05%2F%25E7%2598%258B%25E5%2582%25B3%25E7%2596%2591%25E4%25BC%25BC%25E5%25A7%259A%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%25BE%259A%25E5%25BA%258A%25E7%2589%2587.jpg&h=6cfc3f82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n姚子羚被爆與夜場老闆Raymond拍拖8個月，除了有床照流出外，外間一直有傳二人的情慾片已流出。不過，子羚先後多次否認有拍過情慾片。言猶在耳，今日WhatsApp就瘋傳一條長達5分鐘的情慾片。片中的女主角，某些角度看上去，的確與姚子羚有幾分相似。不過，片中的女子頭髮長至近腰，而姚子羚過去一年除了在台慶頒獎禮上以駁髮形象出現外，均是長至及肩，成了此片疑點<br />\n<br />\n片 <a href=\"http://iso2.cx/view2/28499\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fiso2.cx%2Fview2%2F28499&d=I3HUAc%2BVzuGSjYFa2O0dWMtxnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=a3679173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://iso2.cx/view2/28499</a>"},{"pid":"d92168f8169b389701b92c5893957187b9a5bf79","tid":1173972,"uid":8572,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:25:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f23c003608a4c3031251a2628240430c39971a36","tid":1173972,"uid":5008,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:29:01.000Z","msg":"Error"},{"pid":"a0bf89c5a7adb533a1b64704d71ad2cdd7a96fde","tid":1173972,"uid":156331,"like":8,"dislike":38,"score":-30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9e55b27eb8664b4817276edeb0cefa6bcfbee9c0","tid":1173972,"uid":252668,"like":16,"dislike":106,"score":-90,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-27T13:29:56.000